## Advanced Combinations and Real-World Cases

### Formatting for Technical Documentation

**API Endpoint:** `POST /api/v1/presentations`

**Required headers:**
- `Authorization: Bearer {{api_token}}`
- `Content-Type: application/json`

**Sample payload:**
```json
{
  "title": "My Presentation",
  "template": "corporate",
  "variables": {
    "presenter": "Ana García",
    "date": "2025-01-15"
  }
}
```

**Successful response** (`200 OK`):
```json
{
  "id": "pres_abc123",
  "status": "created",
  "url": "https://slides.company.com/pres_abc123"
}
```

