## Final Quality Checklist

### ✅ **Formatting Verification**

- [ ] **Headings** follow a logical hierarchy (H1→H2→H3)
- [ ] **Paragraphs** have appropriate length (3-5 lines)
- [ ] **Lists** are well nested and organized
- [ ] **Links** have descriptive text
- [ ] **Code** has appropriate syntax highlighting
- [ ] **Images** include alt text and captions
- [ ] **Variables** are correctly referenced
- [ ] **Quotes** have proper attribution
- [ ] **Special blocks** use the correct type
- [ ] **Separators** create clear visual structure

### ✅ **Content Verification**

- [ ] **Main message** is clear and direct
- [ ] **Critical information** is appropriately highlighted
- [ ] **Narrative flow** is logical and progressive
- [ ] **Calls to action** are specific and measurable
- [ ] **Data** is up to date and accurate
- [ ] **Testimonials** are relevant and credible
- [ ] **Benefits** are quantified when possible
- [ ] **Next steps** are clearly defined

